An astronaut crash lands on a mysterious planet only to discover he's not alone.

name: 97 Minutes
description: A hijacked 767 will crash in just 97 minutes when its fuel runs out. Against the strong will of NSA Deputy Toyin, NSA Director Hawkins prepares to have the plane shot down before it does ...                See full summary »

name: На секретной службе Ее Величества

name: Первобытный страх

name: Мстители: Династия Канга
description: Plot under wraps.

name: Любовник леди Чаттерлей

name: Марс атакует!
description: Earth is invaded by Martians with unbeatable weapons and a cruel sense of humor.

name: Кунг Фьюри 2
description: The story will focus on Kung Fury's universe with no real connection to the short movie other than the lead character.

name: Три билборда на границе Эббинга, Миссури

name: Ambush

name: Клаустрофобы
description: Six strangers find themselves in a maze of deadly mystery rooms and must use their wits to survive.

name: Соник в кино
description: After discovering a small, blue, fast hedgehog, a small-town police officer must help him defeat an evil genius who wants to do experiments on him.

name: Школа добра и зла

name: Пустой человек

name: Однажды на Диком Западе

name: Парни со стволами

name: Пункт назначения

When he suddenly has a premonition their airplane will crash, he screams to warn the others but instead he is thrown off of the plane along others, but the plane actually crashes after they get off. Weeks later one of the survivors mysteriously dies, and Alex realizes that things just got more complex.

name: Обливион

name: Патриот

name: Сделка с дьяволом

name: Комната

name: Малышка Руби

name: Мстители: Секретные войны
description: Plot under wraps.

name: Молодой Франкенштейн

name: Превосходство Борна
description: When Jason Bourne is framed for a CIA operation gone awry, he is forced to resume his former life as a trained assassin to survive.

name: Yesterday
description: A struggling musician realizes he's the only person on Earth who can remember The Beatles after waking up in an alternate reality where they never existed.

name: Летняя школа
description: Freddy the gym teacher has to teach remedial English in summer (high) school, if he wants tenure. As he can only teach gym and his students want fun, emphasis is on "field trips" - until he's fired unless all his students pass the test.

name: Симулянт
description: A young guy's only option to erase a really bad debt is to rig the Special Olympics by posing as a contestant.

name: Проверка
description: A young, gay Black man, rejected by his mother and with few options for his future, decides to join the Marines, doing whatever it takes to succeed in a system that would cast him aside.

name: Рискованный бизнес
description: A Chicago teenager is looking for fun at home while his parents are away, but the situation quickly gets out of hand.

name: Оружейный барон
description: An arms dealer confronts the morality of his work as he is being chased by an INTERPOL Agent.

name: Хеллбой II: Золотая армия
description: A prince of the mythical world starts a rebellion against humanity in order to rule the Earth. Hellboy and his team must fight to stop him from locating the all-powerful Golden Army.

name: Багровая мята
description: Five years after her husband and daughter are killed in a senseless act of violence, a woman comes back from self-imposed exile to seek revenge against those responsible and the system that let them go free.

name: Планета обезьян: Революция
description: The fragile peace between apes and humans is threatened as mistrust and betrayal threaten to plunge both tribes into a war for dominance over the Earth.

name: Тошнит от себя
description: Increasingly overshadowed by her boyfriend's recent rise to fame as a contemporary artist creating sculptures from stolen furniture, Signe hatches a vicious plan to reclaim her rightfully deserved attention within the milieu of Oslo's cultural elite.

name: Мост в Терабитию
description: A preteen's life turns upside down when he befriends the new girl in school and they imagine a whole new fantasy world to escape reality.

name: Элизиум: Рай не на Земле
description: In the year 2154, the very wealthy live on a man-made space station while the rest of the population resides on a ruined Earth. A man takes on a mission that could bring equality to the polarized worlds.

name: Дом странных детей Мисс Перегрин
description: When Jacob (Asa Butterfield) discovers clues to a mystery that stretches across time, he finds Miss Peregrine's Home for Peculiar Children. But the danger deepens after he gets to know the residents and learns about their special powers.

name: Роман с камнем
description: A mousy romance novelist sets off for Colombia to ransom her kidnapped sister, and soon finds herself in the middle of a dangerous adventure hunting for treasure with a mercenary rogue.

name: Эквилибриум
description: In an oppressive future where all forms of feeling are illegal, a man in charge of enforcing the law rises to overthrow the system and state.

name: Малые часы
description: In the Middle Ages, a young servant fleeing from his master takes refuge at a convent full of emotionally unstable nuns. Introduced as a deaf mute man, he must fight to hold his cover as the nuns try to resist temptation.

name: Вход в пустоту
description: An American drug dealer living in Tokyo is betrayed by his best friend and killed in a drug deal. His soul, observing the repercussions of his death, seeks resurrection.

name: The Iron Claw
description: Follows the story of the Von Erichs, a dynasty of wrestlers who made a great impact on the sport from the 1960s to the present day.

name: Кот в Сапогах
description: An outlaw cat, his childhood egg-friend, and a seductive thief kitty set out in search for the eggs of the fabled Golden Goose to clear his name, restore his lost honor, and regain the trust of his mother and town.

name: Парк юрского периода III
description: A decidedly odd couple with ulterior motives convince Dr. Grant to go to Isla Sorna for a holiday, but their unexpected landing startles the island's new inhabitants.

name: Люди в чёрном 2
description: Agent Jay is sent to find Agent Kay and restore his memory after the re-appearance of a case from Kay's past.

name: Дальше живите сами
description: After their father passes away, four grown siblings are forced to return to their childhood home and live under the same roof for a week, along with their over-sharing mother and an assortment of spouses, exes, and might-have-beens.

name: Два ствола
description: Two hardened criminals get into trouble with the US border patrol after meeting with a Mexican drug lord, and then revelations start to unfold.

name: Поворот не туда: Наследие
description: Friends hiking the Appalachian Trail are confronted by 'The Foundation', a community of people who have lived in the mountains for hundreds of years.

name: Спеши любить
description: Two North Carolina teens, Landon Carter and Jamie Sullivan, are thrown together after Landon gets into trouble and is sentenced to perform community service.

name: Все леди делают это
description: After five years of marriage, Diana discovers the joys of adultery, claiming that she can save her failing relationship through betrayal.

name: Дик Трэйси
description: The comic strip detective finds his life vastly complicated when Breathless Mahoney makes advances towards him while he is trying to battle Big Boy Caprice's united mob.

name: Парни что надо
description: The U.S. space program's development from the breaking of the sound barrier to selection of the Mercury 7 astronauts, from a group of test pilots with a more seat-of-the-pants approach than the program's more cautious engineers preferred.

name: Ребенок Розмари
description: A young couple trying for a baby moves into an aging, ornate apartment building on Central Park West, where they find themselves surrounded by peculiar neighbors.

name: Хоббит: Битва пяти воинств
description: Bilbo and company are forced to engage in a war against an array of combatants and keep the Lonely Mountain from falling into the hands of a rising darkness.

name: После прочтения сжечь
description: A disk containing mysterious information from a CIA agent ends up in the hands of two unscrupulous and daft gym employees who attempt to sell it.

name: Рейд
description: A S.W.A.T. team becomes trapped in a tenement run by a ruthless mobster and his army of killers and thugs.

name: Комната
description: In San Francisco, an amiable banker's seemingly perfect life is turned upside down when his deceitful fiancée embarks on an affair with his best friend.

name: Борат
description: Kazakh TV talking head Borat is dispatched to the United States to report on the greatest country in the world. With a documentary crew in tow, Borat becomes more interested in locating and marrying Pamela Anderson.

name: Линкольн
description: As the American Civil War continues to rage, America's president struggles with continuing carnage on the battlefield as he fights with many inside his own cabinet on the decision to emancipate the slaves.

name: Мозги набекрень
description: A brain surgeon marries a femme fatale, causing his life to turn upside down. Things go more awry when he falls in love with a talking brain.

name: Война Богов: Бессмертные
description: Theseus is a mortal man chosen by Zeus to lead the fight against the ruthless King Hyperion, who is on a rampage across Greece to obtain a weapon that can destroy humanity.

name: Ральф
description: A video game villain wants to be a hero and sets out to fulfill his dream, but his quest brings havoc to the whole arcade where he lives.

name: Фото за час
description: A mentally unstable photo developer targets an upper middle-class family after his obsession with them becomes more sick and disturbing than any of them could imagine.

name: Звёздные врата
description: An interstellar teleportation device, found in Egypt, leads to a planet with humans resembling ancient Egyptians who worship the god Ra.

name: Остин Пауэрс: Шпион, который меня соблазнил
description: Dr. Evil is back and has invented a new time machine that allows him to go back to the 1960s and steal Austin Powers' mojo, inadvertently leaving him "shagless".

name: Подарок
description: A married couple, Simon and Robyn, run into Gordo, an old classmate. Things take a turn when Gordo begins to drop in unannounced at their house and inundates them with mysterious gifts.

name: Больше, чем секс
description: A guy and girl try to keep their relationship strictly physical, but it's not long before they learn that they want something more.

name: Очень страшное кино 2
description: Four teens are tricked by Professor Oldman (Tim Curry) into visiting a haunted house for a school project.

name: Пятница 13-е
description: A group of young adults visit a boarded up campsite named Crystal Lake where they soon encounter the mysterious Jason Voorhees and his deadly intentions.

name: Сыновья Кэти Элдер
description: Ranch owner Katie Elder's four sons determine to avenge the murder of their father and the swindling of their mother.

name: Kona Coast
description: To avenge the death of his murdered daughter, charter boat captain Sam Moran becomes a one-man vigilante squad taking on the wealthy, drugged-up punk that killed her.

name: Клеопатра
description: Queen Cleopatra VII of Egypt experiences both triumph and tragedy as she attempts to resist the imperial ambitions of Rome.

name: Дикая
description: A chronicle of one woman's 1,100-mile solo hike undertaken as a way to recover from a recent personal tragedy.

name: Вторая жизнь Уве
description: Ove, an ill-tempered, isolated retiree who spends his days enforcing block association rules and visiting his wife's grave, has finally given up on life just as an unlikely friendship develops with his boisterous new neighbors.

name: Астрал. Онлайн
description: Six friends hire a medium to hold a seance via Zoom during lockdown, but they get far more than they bargained for as things quickly go wrong.

name: Shin Kamen Rider
description: Hongo Takeshi awakens to discover he has been transformed into a grasshopper-hybrid cyborg. Becoming the Masked Rider, he must fight the mysterious evil organization SHOCKER to protect all of mankind.

name: Козырные тузы
description: When a Las Vegas performer-turned-snitch named Buddy Israel decides to turn state's evidence and testify against the mob, it seems that a whole lot of people would like to make sure he's no longer breathing.

name: Джонни и Клайд
description: Johnny and Clyde are two serial killers who are madly in love and on an endless crime spree. They have their sights set on robbing a prosperous casino - owned by crime boss Alana and guarded by a demonic slayer that she commands.

name: Грань времени
description: Two New Orleans paramedics' lives are ripped apart after they encounter a series of horrific deaths linked to a designer drug with bizarre, otherworldly effects.

name: Шеф Адам Джонс
description: Adam Jones is a chef who destroyed his career with drugs and diva behavior. He cleans up and returns to London, determined to redeem himself by spearheading a top restaurant that can gain three Michelin stars.

name: Энола Холмс 2
description: Now a detective-for-hire, Enola Holmes takes on her first official case to find a missing girl as the sparks of a dangerous conspiracy ignite a mystery that requires the help of friends - and Sherlock himself - to unravel.

name: Убить пересмешника
description: Atticus Finch, a widowed lawyer in Depression-era Alabama, defends a Black man against an undeserved rape charge, and tries to educate his young children against prejudice.

name: Мистер и миссис Смит
description: A bored married couple is surprised to learn that they are both assassins hired by competing agencies to kill each other.

name: Страна чудес Вилли
description: A quiet drifter is tricked into a janitorial job at the now condemned Willy's Wonderland. The mundane tasks suddenly become an all-out fight for survival against wave after wave of demonic animatronics. Fists fly, kicks land, titans clash -- and only one side will make it out alive.

name: Профессор и призрачный убийца
description: A detective on the verge of retirement teams with a professor of African Studies to track down a serial killer who is performing the ancient black magic practice of Muti.

name: Истинная грусть
description: A pop singer gives up her career to become an actress, but she slowly goes insane when she starts being stalked by an obsessed fan and what seems to be a ghost of her past.

name: Огни святого Эльма
description: A group of friends, just out of college, struggle with adulthood.

name: Робин Гуд: Мужчины в трико
description: A spoof of Robin Hood in general, and Робин Гуд: Принц воров (1991) in particular.

name: Мальчик в полосатой пижаме
description: Through the innocent eyes of Bruno, the eight-year-old son of the commandant at a German concentration camp, a forbidden friendship with a Jewish boy on the other side of the camp fence has startling and unexpected consequences.

name: Сонная Лощина
description: Ichabod Crane is sent to Sleepy Hollow to investigate the decapitations of three people; the culprit is legendary apparition The Headless Horseman.

name: Телекинез
description: A shy girl, outcast by her peers and sheltered by her religious mother, unleashes telekinetic terror on her small town after being pushed too far at her senior prom.

name: Головокружение
description: A former San Francisco police detective juggles wrestling with his personal demons and becoming obsessed with the hauntingly beautiful woman he has been hired to trail, who may be deeply disturbed.

name: Мэнди
description: The enchanted lives of a couple in a secluded forest are brutally shattered by a nightmarish hippie cult and their demon-biker henchmen, propelling a man into a spiraling, surreal rampage of vengeance.

name: Святая Гора
description: In a corrupt, greed-fueled world, a powerful alchemist leads a messianic character and seven materialistic figures to the Holy Mountain, where they hope to achieve enlightenment.

name: Основатель
description: The story of Ray Kroc, a salesman who turned two brothers' innovative fast food eatery, McDonald's, into the biggest restaurant business in the world, with a combination of ambition, persistence, and ruthlessness.

name: Ровно в полдень
description: A town Marshal, despite the disagreements of his newlywed bride and the townspeople around him, must face a gang of deadly killers alone at "high noon" when the gang leader, an outlaw he "sent up" years ago, arrives on the noon train.

name: Стальной гигант
description: A young boy befriends a giant robot from outer space that a paranoid government agent wants to destroy.

name: Хроники Риддика
description: The wanted criminal Richard Bruno Riddick arrives on a planet called Helion Prime and finds himself up against an invading empire called the Necromongers, an army that plans to convert or kill all humans in the universe.

name: Смертельное оружие
description: Two newly paired cops who are complete opposites must put aside their differences in order to catch a gang of drug smugglers.

name: Малефисента 2: Владычица тьмы
description: Maleficent and her goddaughter Aurora begin to question the complex family ties that bind them as they are pulled in different directions by impending nuptials, unexpected allies, and dark new forces at play.

name: Боги Египта
description: Mortal hero Bek teams with the god Horus in an alliance against Set, the merciless god of darkness, who has usurped Egypt's throne, plunging the once peaceful and prosperous empire into chaos and conflict.

name: Джонни Д.
description: The Feds try to take down notorious American gangsters John Dillinger, Baby Face Nelson, and Pretty Boy Floyd during a booming crime wave in the 1930s.

name: Университет монстров
description: A look at the relationship between Mike Wazowski (Billy Crystal) and James P. "Sully" Sullivan (John Goodman) during their days at Monsters University, when they weren't necessarily the best of friends.

name: Формула любви для узников брака
description: A comedy centered around four couples who settle into a tropical-island resort for a vacation. While one of the couples is there to work on the marriage, the others fail to realize that participation in the resort's therapy sessions is not optional.

name: 13 жизней
description: A rescue mission is assembled in Thailand where a group of young boys and their soccer coach are trapped in a system of underground caves that are flooding.

name: В осаде
description: An ex-Navy Seal turned cook is the only person who can stop a group of terrorists when they seize control of a U.S. battleship.

name: И пришел паук
description: When a senator's daughter under Secret Service protection is kidnapped from a private school, detective Alex Cross investigates the case even though he's recovering from the loss of his partner.

name: Банк Дэйва
description: Based on the true-life experiences of Dave Fishwick; 'Bank of Dave' tells the story of how a working class Burnley man and self-made millionaire fought to set up a community bank.

name: Убойные каникулы
description: Affable hillbillies Tucker and Dale are on vacation at their dilapidated mountain cabin when they are mistaken for murderers by a group of preppy college students.

name: Призрак в доспехах
description: In the near future, Major Mira Killian is the first of her kind: A human saved from a terrible crash, who is cyber-enhanced to be a perfect soldier devoted to stopping the world's most dangerous criminals.

name: Планета страха
description: After an experimental bio-weapon is released, turning thousands into zombie-like creatures, it's up to a rag-tag group of survivors to stop the infected and those behind its release.

name: Невероятные приключения Билла и Теда
description: Two rock-'n-rolling teens, on the verge of failing their class, set out on a quest to make the ultimate school history report after being presented with a time machine.

name: После работы
description: An ordinary word processor has the worst night of his life after he agrees to visit a girl in Soho he met that evening at a coffee shop.

name: Облачно, возможны осадки в виде фрикаделек
description: A local scientist is often regarded as a failure until he invents a machine that can make food fall from the sky. But little does he know that things are about to take a turn for the worst.

name: Луна 2112
description: Astronaut Sam Bell has a quintessentially personal encounter toward the end of his three-year stint on the Moon, where he, working alongside his computer, GERTY, sends back to Earth parcels of a resource that has helped diminish our planet's power problems.

name: Большая жратва
description: Young employees at ShenaniganZ restaurant collectively stave off boredom and adulthood with their antics.

name: Планета обезьян
description: In 2029, an Air Force astronaut crash-lands on a mysterious planet where evolved, talking apes dominate a race of primitive humans.

name: Воспоминание
description: Nick Bannister, a private investigator of the mind, navigates the alluring world of the past when his life is changed by new client Mae. A simple case becomes an obsession after she disappears and he fights to learn the truth about her.

name: Поле чудес
description: Iowa farmer Ray Kinsella is inspired by a voice he can't ignore to pursue a dream he can hardly believe. Supported by his wife, Ray begins the quest by turning his ordinary cornfield into a place where dreams can come true.

name: Барбарелла
description: Barbarella, an astronaut from the 41st century, sets out to find and stop the evil scientist Durand Durand, whose Positronic Ray threatens to bring evil back into the galaxy.

name: Прорва
description: A young couple struggles to repair a hopelessly dilapidated house.

name: Побег из курятника
description: When a cockerel apparently flies into a chicken farm, the chickens see him as an opportunity to escape their evil owners.

name: Тор 2: Царство тьмы
description: When the Dark Elves attempt to plunge the universe into darkness, Thor must embark on a perilous and personal journey that will reunite him with doctor Jane Foster.

name: Трон
description: A computer hacker is abducted into the digital world and forced to participate in gladiatorial games where his only chance of escape is with the help of a heroic security program.

name: Кавалерия
description: 12 Strong tells the story of the first Special Forces team deployed to Afghanistan after 9/11; under the leadership of a new captain, the team must work with an Afghan warlord to take down the Taliban.

name: Возможности карьеры
description: Jim is the dorky son of a local cement contractor who lives at home and has no direction. Josie is the gorgeous daughter of a wealthy businessman who dreams of leaving town. They find they have a lot in common.

name: Молодая Виктория
description: A dramatization of the turbulent first years of Queen Victoria's rule, and her enduring romance with Prince Albert.

name: Подземелье драконов
description: Profion, a tyrant, attempts to overthrow a peaceful kingdom ruled by a tough empress.

name: Поезд на Дарджилинг. Отчаянные путешественники
description: A year after their father's funeral, three brothers travel across India by train in an attempt to bond with each other.

name: Белфаст
description: A young boy and his working-class Belfast family experience the tumultuous late 1960s.

name: Городские легенды
description: A college student suspects a series of bizarre deaths are connected to certain urban legends.

name: Тайна 7 сестёр
description: In a world where families are limited to one child due to overpopulation, a set of identical septuplets must avoid being put to a long sleep by the government and dangerous infighting while investigating the disappearance of one of their own.

name: The Evil of Dracula
description: A professor takes up a new post at an all-girls school only to discover the school's principle conceals a dark secret and the pupils are in grave danger.

name: Как малые дети
description: The lives of two lovelorn spouses from separate marriages, a registered sex offender, and a disgraced ex-police officer intersect as they struggle to resist their vulnerabilities and temptations in suburban Massachusetts.

name: Побег из Нью-Йорка
description: In 1997, when the U.S. president crashes into Manhattan, now a giant maximum security prison, a convicted bank robber is sent in to rescue him.

name: The Flood
description: A daring jail break during a dangerous Louisiana hurricane is interrupted by a horde of large hungry alligators.

name: План побега
description: When a structural-security authority finds himself set up and incarcerated in the world's most secret and secure prison, he has to use his skills to escape with help from the inside.

name: Барри Линдон
description: An Irish rogue wins the heart of a rich widow and assumes her dead husband's aristocratic position in 18th-century England.

name: Девушка по соседству
description: Follows the unspeakable torture and abuses committed on a teenage girl in the care of her aunt and the boys who witness and fail to report the crime.

name: Титан
description: Following a series of unexplained crimes, a father is reunited with the son who has been missing for 10 years.

name: Астрал 4: Последний ключ
description: Parapsychologist Dr. Elise Rainier faces her most fearsome and personal haunting yet, as she is drawn back to her ghostly childhood home where the terror began.

name: Сын Кавери: Часть вторая
description: Arulmozhi Varman continues on his journey to become Rajaraja I, the greatest ruler of the historic Chola empire of south India.

name: Дело о пеликанах
description: A law student uncovers a conspiracy, putting herself and others in danger.

name: Иллюзия обмана 2
description: The Four Horsemen resurface, and are forcibly recruited by a tech genius to pull off their most impossible heist yet.

name: Загон для собак
description: Three juvenile delinquents are sentenced to a correctional facility where they encounter gang violence, death, and harassment from staff and other inmates.

name: Мой сосед Тоторо
description: When two girls move to the country to be near their ailing mother, they have adventures with the wondrous forest spirits who live nearby.

name: Квадрат
description: A prestigious Stockholm museum's chief art curator finds himself in times of both professional and personal crisis as he attempts to set up a controversial new exhibit.

name: Тачки 3
description: Lightning McQueen sets out to prove to a new generation of racers that he's still the best race car in the world.

name: My Big Fat Greek Wedding 3
description: Join the Portokalos family as they travel to a family reunion in Greece for a heartwarming and hilarious trip full of love, twists and turns.

name: The Best Man
description: Mercenaries seize control of a remote resort hotel during a wedding and it's up to the best man, the groom and their drunken best friend to stop the terrorists and save the hostages.

name: Джек Ричер 2: Никогда не возвращайся
description: Jack Reacher must uncover the truth behind a major government conspiracy in order to clear his name while on the run as a fugitive from the law.

name: Баффи - истребительница вампиров
description: Flighty teenage girl Buffy Summers learns that she is her generation's destined battler of vampires.

name: Вспомнить всё
description: A factory worker, Douglas Quaid, begins to suspect that he is a spy after visiting Rekall - a company that provides its clients with implanted fake memories of a life they would like to have led - goes wrong and he finds himself on the run.

name: Книга Илая
description: A post-apocalyptic tale, in which a lone man fights his way across America in order to protect a sacred book that holds the secrets to saving humankind.

name: Грязная дюжина
description: During World War II, a rebellious U.S. Army Major is assigned a dozen convicted murderers to train and lead them into a mass assassination mission of German officers.

name: Гонки «Пушечное ядро»
description: A wide variety of eccentric competitors participate in a wild and illegal cross-country road race. However, the eccentric entrants will do anything to win the road race, including low-down, dirty tricks.

name: Это безумный, безумный, безумный, безумный мир
description: A group of motorists witnesses a car crash in the California desert, and after the driver's dying words indicate the location of a hidden stash of loot, they turn against each in a race across the state to get to it.

name: Шпионский мост
description: During the Cold War, an American lawyer is recruited to defend an arrested Soviet spy in court, and then help the CIA facilitate an exchange of the spy for the Soviet captured American U2 spy plane pilot, Francis Gary Powers.

name: Секс в большом городе
description: A New York City writer on sex and love is finally getting married to her Mr. Big. But her three best girlfriends must console her after one of them inadvertently leads Mr. Big to jilt her.

name: Незваные гости
description: John Beckwith and Jeremy Grey, a pair of committed womanizers who sneak into weddings to take advantage of the romantic tinge in the air, find themselves at odds with one another when John meets and falls for Claire Cleary.

name: Дневная смена
description: A hard-working, blue-collar dad just wants to provide a good life for his quick-witted 10-year-old daughter. His mundane San Fernando Valley pool cleaning job is a front for his real source of income: hunting and killing vampires.

name: Уйти красиво
description: Desperate to pay the bills and come through for their loved ones, three lifelong pals risk it all by embarking on a daring bid to knock off the very bank that absconded with their money.

name: Туристический путеводитель по любви
description: An executive goes through an unexpected breakup, then accepting an assignment to go undercover and learn about the tourist industry in Vietnam.

name: Викрам Веда
description: A tough police officer sets out to track down and kill an equally tough gangster.

name: Черепашки-ниндзя 2
description: The Turtles get into another battle with their enemy the Shredder, who has acquired new allies: the mutant thugs Bebop and Rocksteady and the alien being Krang.

name: Поступь хаоса
description: Two unlikely companions embark on a perilous adventure through the badlands of an unexplored planet as they try to escape a dangerous and disorienting reality where all thoughts are seen and heard by everyone.

name: Тем больнее падать
description: When an outlaw discovers his enemy is being released from prison, he reunites his gang to seek revenge.

name: Разрушение
description: A successful investment banker struggles after losing his wife in a tragic car crash. With the help of a customer service rep and her young son, he starts to rebuild, beginning with the demolition of the life he once knew.

name: В случае убийства набирайте «М»
description: A former tennis star arranges the murder of his adulterous wife.

name: Сумерки. Сага. Рассвет: Часть 1
description: The Quileutes close in on expecting parents Edward and Bella, whose unborn child poses a threat to the Wolf Pack and the towns people of Forks.

name: Евровидение: История группы Fire Saga
description: When aspiring musicians Lars and Sigrit are given the opportunity to represent their country at the world's biggest song competition, they finally have a chance to prove that any dream worth having is a dream worth fighting for.

name: Аргайл
description: The world's greatest spy, 'Argylle,' gets caught up in a globe-trotting adventure.

name: Лемони Сникет: 33 несчастья
description: When a massive fire kills their parents, three children are delivered to the custody of cousin and stage actor Count Olaf, who is secretly plotting to steal their parents' vast fortune.

name: Крепкий орешек 4.0
description: John McClane and a young hacker join forces to take down master cyber-terrorist Thomas Gabriel in Washington D.C.

name: S.W.A.T.: Спецназ города ангелов
description: An imprisoned drug kingpin offers a huge cash reward to anyone that can break him out of police custody, and only the L.A.P.D.'s Special Weapons and Tactics team can prevent it.

name: Смерть Сталина
description: Moscow, 1953. After being in power for nearly 30 years, Soviet dictator Joseph Vissarionovich Stalin takes ill and quickly dies. Now the members of the Council of Ministers scramble for power.

name: Рожденный четвертого июля
description: The biography of Ron Kovic. Paralyzed in the Vietnam war, he becomes an anti-war and pro-human rights political activist after feeling betrayed by the country for which he fought.

name: Росомаха: Бессмертный
description: Wolverine comes to Japan to meet an old friend whose life he saved years ago, and gets embroiled in a conspiracy involving yakuza and mutants.

name: Робин Гуд

name: Godzilla x Kong: The New Empire
description: Plot kept under wraps.

Stopping at a Viking village port to restock on supplies, he finds himself unwittingly embroiled in a quest to banish a mysterious threat in a distant Viking land.

description: It is said that every investigator has a crime that haunts them, a case that hurts him more than the others, without him necessarily knowing why. For Yohan that case is the murder of Clara.

name: Целитель Адамс
description: The true story of a heroic man, Hunter "Patch" Adams, determined to become a medical doctor because he enjoys helping people. He ventured where no doctor had ventured before, using humour and pathos.

name: Бремя
description: After an epidemic spreads all over Australia, a father searches for someone willing to protect his daughter.

name: Страна призраков
description: A mother of two who inherits a house is confronted with murderous intruders on the first night in their new home and fights for her daughters' lives. Sixteen years later when the daughters reunite at the house, things get really strange.

name: Призрачный мир
description: With only the plan of moving in together after high school, two unusually devious friends seek direction in life. As a mere gag, they respond to a man's newspaper ad for a date, only to find it will greatly complicate their lives.

name: Горячее местечко
description: Upon arriving to a small town, a drifter quickly gets into trouble with the local authorities - and the local women - after he robs a bank.

name: Лок
description: Ivan Locke, a dedicated family man and successful construction manager, receives a phone call on the eve of the biggest challenge of his career that sets in motion a series of events that threaten his carefully cultivated existence.

name: Дорогой Джон
description: A romantic drama about a soldier who falls for a conservative college student while he's home on leave.

name: Ничего себе поездочка
description: Three young people on a road trip from Colorado to New Jersey talk to a trucker on their CB radio, then must escape when he turns out to be a psychopathic killer.

name: Из прошлого

name: Клуб Shortbus

name: Оно приходит ночью
description: Secure within a desolate home as an unnatural threat terrorizes the world, a man has established a tenuous domestic order with his wife and son. Then a desperate young family arrives seeking refuge.

name: Голый пистолет

name: Твои, мои и наши
description: A widowed Coast Guard Admiral and a widowed handbag designer fall in love and marry, much to the dismay of his 8 and her 10 children.

name: Легион супергероев

name: Четыре хороших дня

name: Энни Холл
description: Alvy Singer, a divorced Jewish comedian, reflects on his relationship with ex-lover Annie Hall, an aspiring nightclub singer, which ended abruptly just like his previous marriages.

name: Солярис
description: A psychologist is sent to a station orbiting a distant planet in order to discover what has caused the crew to go insane.

name: Дом

name: Пятница 13 - Часть 3
description: Jason Voorhees stalks a group of friends who's just arrived to spend the weekend at a cabin near Crystal Lake.

name: Радиоволна

name: Убийства в Оксфорде

name: Обед нагишом
description: After developing an addiction to the substance he uses to kill bugs, an exterminator accidentally kills his wife, and becomes involved in a secret government plot being orchestrated by giant bugs in a port town in North Africa.

name: Врата рая

name: День 'Д', шестое июня

name: Франкеншлюха

name: Дорз

name: Под солнцем Тосканы
description: A writer impulsively buys a villa in Tuscany in order to change her life.

name: Репродукция
description: A scientist becomes obsessed with bringing back his family members who died in a traffic accident.

name: Bлaстелин колец
description: The Fellowship of the Ring embark on a journey to destroy the One Ring and end Sauron's reign over Middle-earth.

name: Спокойной ночи, мамочка
description: Twin brothers arrive at their mother's house and begin to suspect that something isn't right.

name: Ущерб
description: A member of Parliament falls passionately in love with his son's fiancée despite the dangers of discovery.

name: Лига монстров
description: In a world where monster wrestling is a global sport and monsters are superstar athletes, teenage Winnie seeks to follow in her father's footsteps by coaching a loveable underdog monster into a champion.

name: Джейсон X

description: The story of James J. Braddock, a supposedly washed-up boxer who came back to challenge for the heavyweight championship of the world.

description: Biographical epic of the controversial and influential Black Nationalist leader, from his early life and career as a small-time gangster, to his ministry as a member of the Nation of Islam and his eventual assassination.

name: Паства

name: Цыплёнок Цыпа
description: After ruining his reputation with the town, a courageous chicken must come to the rescue of his fellow citizens when aliens start an invasion.

name: Почему он?

name: Вeрдикт
description: An outcast, alcoholic Boston lawyer sees the chance to salvage his career and self-respect by taking a medical malpractice case to trial rather than settling.

name: Шоколад

name: Общество Онор

name: Я Сэм
description: A mentally handicapped man fights for custody of his 7-year-old daughter and in the process teaches his cold-hearted lawyer the value of love and family.

name: Яйцеголовые

name: Пропавшая
description: In 1885 New Mexico, a frontier medicine woman forms an uneasy alliance with her estranged father when her daughter is kidnapped by an Apache brujo.

name: Призрачный патруль 2: Восстание проклятых
description: Recruited by the R.I.P.D., a resurrected sheriff returns to Earth to save humanity from a gateway to hell.

name: Европейские каникулы
description: The Griswolds win a vacation tour across Europe where the usual havoc ensues.

name: Возвращение в Голубую лагуну
description: In this sequel to Голубая лагуна (1980), two children are stranded on a beautiful island in the South Pacific. With no adults to guide them, the two make a simple life together and eventually become suntanned teenagers in love.

name: Гордость и предубеждение и зомби
description: Five sisters in 19th century England must cope with the pressures to marry while protecting themselves from a growing population of zombies.

name: The Old Guard 2
description: Plot Unknown. Sequel to Бессмертная гвардия (2020).

name: Братья Лейлы
description: At the age of 40, Leila has spent her entire life caring for her parents and four brothers. A family that is constantly arguing and under pressure from various debts in the face of ...                See full summary »

name: Крысиные бега
description: A Las Vegas casino magnate, determined to find a new avenue for wagering, sets up a race for money.

name: Джули и Джулия: Готовим счастье по рецепту
description: Julia Child's story of her start in the cooking profession is intertwined with blogger Julie Powell's 2002 challenge to cook all the recipes in Child's first book.

name: Возлюбленные
description: A troubled couple vacate to a beautiful getaway, but bizarre circumstances further complicate their situation.

name: Знакомство с Факерами
description: All hell breaks loose when the Byrnes family meets the Focker family for the first time.

name: Разоблачение
description: A computer specialist is sued for sexual harassment by a former lover turned boss who initiated the act forcefully, which threatens both his career and his personal life.

name: Амистад

name: Капоте

name: Остров доктора Моро
description: After being rescued and brought to an island, a man discovers that its inhabitants are experimental animals being turned into strange-looking humans, all of it the work of a visionary doctor.

name: Рэй
description: The story of the life and career of the legendary rhythm and blues musician Ray Charles, from his humble beginnings in the South, where he went blind at age seven, to his meteoric rise to stardom during the 1950s and 1960s.

name: Дневник пастыря

name: В этом мире я больше не чувствую себя как дома
description: When a depressed woman is burgled, she finds a new sense of purpose by tracking down the thieves alongside her obnoxious neighbour. But they soon find themselves dangerously out of their depth against a pack of degenerate criminals.

name: Никогда не сдавайся

name: Соломенные псы
description: A young American and his English wife come to rural England and face increasingly vicious local harassment.

name: Дорога на Эльдорадо
description: Two swindlers get their hands on a map to the fabled city of gold, El Dorado.

name: История Золушки
description: Routinely exploited by her wicked stepmother, the downtrodden Samantha Montgomery is excited about the prospect of meeting her Internet beau at the school's Halloween dance.

name: Первобытный

name: Отчаянный ход
description: Thirty-four years after his death, Airman William H. "Pits" Pitsenbarger is awarded the nation's highest military honor for his actions on the battlefield.

name: Затура: Космическое приключение
description: Two young brothers are drawn into an intergalactic adventure when their house is hurled through the depths of space by the magical board game they are playing.

name: Месть от кутюр
description: A glamorous woman returns to her small town in rural Australia. With her sewing machine and haute couture style, she transforms the women and exacts sweet revenge on those who did her wrong.

name: Волшебник
description: A boy and his brother run away from home and hitch cross-country, with help from a girl they meet, to compete in the ultimate video-game championship.

name: 28 днeй
description: A big-city newspaper columnist is forced to enter a drug and alcohol rehab center after ruining her sister's wedding and crashing a stolen limousine.

name: Просто друзья

name: Сожжение

name: Полет навигатора
description: In 1978, a boy travels eight years into the future and has an adventure with an intelligent, wisecracking alien ship.

name: Ночь охотника
description: A religious fanatic marries a gullible widow whose young children are reluctant to tell him where their real daddy hid the $10,000 he'd stolen in a robbery.

name: Подводный дом

name: Лес призраков

name: Смывайся!
description: The story of an uptown rat that gets flushed down the toilet from his penthouse apartment, ending in the sewers of London, where he has to learn a whole new and different way of life.

name: Порочные игры

name: На лоне природы

name: Смерть на похоронах
description: A funeral ceremony turns into a debacle of exposed family secrets and misplaced bodies.

name: Вердикт за деньги

name: Свояки
description: On the eve of their children's marriage, NYC in-laws Sheldon Kornpett and Vince Ricardo embark on a series of misadventures involving the CIA, the Treasury Department and Central American dictators.

name: Отец невесты

name: Приключения Джо Грязнули
description: After being abandoned by his parents at the Grand Canyon, Joe Dirt tells the story of his journey to find his parents.

name: Травма
description: Four friends, partying in a house in the middle of nowhere are brutally attacked by a man and his son, forcing the remaining women to take vengeance upon them.

name: Королева проклятых
description: In this loose sequel to Интервью с вампиром (1994), the vampire Lestat becomes a rock star whose music wakes up the equally beautiful and monstrous queen of all vampires.

name: Вальдо
description: A disgraced ex-cop seeks solace by moving to the woods, but his quiet life comes to an end when a private eye recruits him to investigate a murder.

name: Божья земля

name: Красотки в бегах
description: An uptight and by-the-book cop (Reese Witherspoon) tries to protect the outgoing widow (Sofia Vergara) of a drug boss as they race through Texas pursued by crooked cops and murderous gunmen.

name: Где моя тачка, чувак?

name: Одинокая белая женщина

name: Розовая пантера
description: Bumbling Inspector Clouseau must solve the murder of a famous soccer coach and find out who stole the infamous Pink Panther diamond.

name: Улица страха. Часть 2: 1978
description: Shadyside, 1978. School's out for summer and the activities at Camp Nightwing are about to begin. But when another Shadysider is possessed with the urge to kill, the fun in the sun becomes a gruesome fight for survival.

name: Ночной рейс
description: A woman is kidnapped by a stranger on a routine flight. Threatened by the potential murder of her father, she is pulled into a plot to assist her captor in a political assassination.

name: Кривая линия
description: A soon-to-be bride on her way to a wedding rehearsal is having second thoughts and decides to take a detour. Car breaks down and a hitchiker offers help. Could it be fate?

name: Жить и умереть в Лос-Анджелесе
description: A fearless Secret Service agent will stop at nothing to bring down the counterfeiter who killed his partner.

name: Август
description: A look at the lives of the strong-willed women of the Weston family, whose paths have diverged until a family crisis brings them back to the Oklahoma house they grew up in, and to the dysfunctional woman who raised them.

name: Туман
description: An unearthly fog rolls into a small coastal town exactly 100 years after a ship mysteriously sank in its waters.

name: Шаровая молния
description: James Bond heads to the Bahamas to recover two nuclear warheads stolen by S.P.E.C.T.R.E. Agent Emilio Largo in an international extortion scheme.

name: Одинокий рейнджер
description: Native American warrior Tonto recounts the untold tales that transformed John Reid, a man of the law, into a legend of justice.

name: Голая правда
description: An uptight television producer takes control of a morning show segment on modern relationships hosted by a misogynistic man.

name: Ужасный доктор Файбс
description: Doctor, scientist, organist, and biblical scholar Anton Phibes seeks revenge on the nine doctors he considers responsible for the death of his wife.

name: The Collective
description: A young recruit to a mysterious agency of assassins finds himself going rogue on his first assignment, tracking down a dangerous group of human traffickers.

name: Бродяга высокогорных равнин
description: A gun-fighting stranger comes to the small settlement of Lago and is hired to bring the townsfolk together in an attempt to hold off three outlaws who are on their way.

name: Убийство в Восточном экспрессе
description: In December 1935, when his transcontinental luxury train is stranded by deep snow, detective Hercule Poirot is called on to solve a murder that occurred in his car the night before, with a multitude of suspects.

name: Призраки прошлого
description: A pregnant woman on bed rest begins to wonder if her house is haunted or it's all in her head.

name: Вторжение динозавра
description: A monster emerges from Seoul's Han River and begins attacking people. One victim's loving family does what it can to rescue her from its clutches.

name: Семейка монстров
description: Reboot of "The Munsters," that followed a family of monsters who moves from Transylvania to an American suburb.

name: Мисс Конгениальность 2: Прекрасна и опасна
description: Gracie Hart abandons the life of a field agent to become the public face of FBI. Yet when Cheryl Frasier and Stan Fields are kidnapped, she is determined to rescue them, along with her reluctant partner.

name: Частная школa

name: Сканнеры
description: A scientist trains a man with an advanced telepathic ability called "scanning" to stop a dangerous Scanner with extraordinary psychic powers from waging war against non scanners.

name: Робин Гуд: Начало
description: A war-hardened Crusader and his Moorish commander mount an audacious revolt against the corrupt English crown.

name: Анатомия убийства
description: An upstate Michigan lawyer defends a soldier who claims he killed an innkeeper due to temporary insanity after the victim raped his wife. What is the truth, and will he win his case?

name: Секс, ложь и видео
description: A sexually repressed woman's husband is having an affair with her sister. The arrival of a visitor with a rather unusual fetish changes everything.

name: Хищник 2
description: The Predator returns to Earth, this time to stake a claim on the war-torn streets of a dystopian Los Angeles.

name: Тайное окно
description: A successful writer in the midst of a painful divorce is stalked at his remote lake house by a would-be scribe who accuses him of plagiarism.

name: Нечто
description: Scientists and American Air Force officials fend off a bloodthirsty alien organism while at a remote arctic outpost.

name: Последний американский девственник
description: Pizza delivery boy Gary, loudmouth David and hunky Rick are three high school students out to lose their virginity any way they can. Gary falls for transfer student Karen, who gets involved with Rick.

name: Райский проект
description: A paroled former criminal is drawn into an endeavor that puts life with his family at risk and subsequently finds himself living an inexplicable new life working at a psychiatric facility.

name: Красные
description: A radical American journalist becomes involved with the Communist revolution in Russia, and hopes to bring its spirit and idealism to the United States.

name: Отель «Руанда»
description: Paul Rusesabagina, a hotel manager, houses over a thousand Tutsi refugees during their struggle against the Hutu militia in Rwanda, Africa.

name: Герой
description: A defense officer, Nameless, was summoned by the King of Qin regarding his success of terminating three warriors.

name: Вулкан
description: A volcano erupts in downtown Los Angeles and a city official and a seismologist try to stop its inevitable flow through the city.

name: Эксперимент 'Офис'
description: In a twisted social experiment, eighty Americans are locked in their high-rise corporate office in Bogotá, Colombia, and ordered by an unknown voice coming from the company's intercom system to participate in a deadly game of kill or be killed.

name: Кровь

name: Достать коротышку
description: A mobster travels to Hollywood to collect a debt, and discovers that the movie business is much the same as his current job.

name: Эван Всемогущий
description: God contacts Congressman Evan Baxter and tells him to build an ark in preparation for a great flood.

name: Воспламеняющая взглядом
description: A young girl tries to understand how she mysteriously gained the power to set things on fire with her mind.

name: Запретная планета

name: Тёмные отражения
description: After a disease kills 98% of children, the survivors develop powers and are declared a threat. 16-year-old Ruby, escapes the government facility and joins a group of rebel teenagers ready to fight the government forces out to get them.

name: Сердце дракона
description: The last dragon and a disillusioned dragonslaying Knight must cooperate to stop an evil King, who was given partial immortality.

name: Группировка «Восток»
description: An operative for an elite private intelligence firm finds her priorities changing dramatically after she is tasked with infiltrating an anarchist group known for executing covert attacks upon major corporations.

name: Проект Power
description: When a pill that gives its users unpredictable superpowers for five minutes hits the streets of New Orleans, a teenage dealer and a local cop must team with an ex-soldier to take down the group responsible for its creation.

name: Снегоуборщик

name: Отец-молодец
description: An affable underachiever finds out he's fathered 533 children through anonymous donations to a fertility clinic 20 years ago. Now he must decide whether or not to come forward when 142 of them file a lawsuit to reveal his identity.

name: Уиджи: Проклятие Вероники
description: Madrid, 1991. A teen girl finds herself besieged by an evil supernatural force after she played Ouija with two classmates.

name: 101 далматинeц

name: Охотник на лис

name: Братец медвежонок
description: When a young Inuit hunter needlessly kills a bear, he is magically changed into a bear himself as punishment with a talkative cub being his only guide to changing back.

name: Мертвая тишина
description: A young widower returns to his hometown to search for answers to his wife's murder, which may be linked to the ghost of a deceased ventriloquist.

name: Генеральская дочь
description: When the daughter of a well-known and well-respected base commander is murdered, an undercover detective is summoned to look into the matter and finds a slew of cover-ups at West Point.

name: Соблазн

name: Жар

name: Человек, который застрелил Либерти Вэланса
description: A senator returns to a Western town for the funeral of an old friend and tells the story of his origins.

name: Жертвуя пешкой
description: Set during the Cold War, American chess prodigy Bobby Fischer finds himself caught between two superpowers and his own struggles as he challenges the Soviet Empire.

name: Астрал: Потомство
description: A young woman tries to find her origins after having been abandoned as an infant at a cemetery wrapped in a cloth with satanic symbols, but as she gets closer to answers a malevolent spirit is telling her to leave.

name: Последний король Шотландии
description: Based on the events of the brutal Ugandan dictator Idi Amin's regime as seen by his personal physician during the 1970s.

name: Клетка

description: A comedic retelling of Shakespeare's "Romeo and Juliet," told from the point of view of Romeo's jilted ex, Rosaline, the woman Romeo first claims to love before he falls for Juliet.

name: Изобретение лжи
description: A comedy set in a world where no one has ever lied, until a writer seizes the opportunity for personal gain.

description: In 2002, two rival Olympic ice skaters were stripped of their gold medals and permanently banned from men's single competition. Presently, however, they've found a loophole that will allow them to qualify as a pairs team.

name: Шафер напрокат
description: Two weeks shy of his wedding, a socially awkward guy enters into a charade by hiring the owner of a company that provides best men for grooms in need.

name: Самый жестокий год
description: In New York City 1981, an ambitious immigrant fights to protect his business and family during the most dangerous year in the city's history.

name: Роман Израэл, Esq.
description: Roman J. Israel, Esq., a driven, idealistic defense attorney, finds himself in a tumultuous series of events that lead to a crisis and the necessity for extreme action.

name: Золото дураков
description: A new clue to the whereabouts of a lost treasure rekindles a married couple's sense of adventure -- and their estranged romance.

name: Ночная тусовка
description: Desperate to improve their social status, four best friends enter into an all-night scavenger hunt against the popular clique in their school.

name: Роми и Мишель на встрече выпускников
description: Two dim-witted, inseparable friends hit the road for their ten-year high school reunion and concoct an elaborate lie about their lives in order to impress their classmates.

name: Джиперс криперс-2

name: Однажды

name: Мистер Дидс переезжает в город
description: A unassuming greeting card poet from a small town in Vermont heads to New York City upon inheriting a massive fortune and is immediately hounded by those who wish to take advantage of him.

name: Ты - моё сомнение
description: Everyone assumed that Sasha and Marcus would wind up together, except for Sasha and Marcus. Reconnecting after 15 years, the two start to wonder--maybe?

name: Одиннадцать друзей Оушена
description: Danny Ocean gathers a group of his World War II compatriots to pull off the ultimate Las Vegas heist. Together the eleven friends plan to rob five Las Vegas casinos in one night.

name: Ма
description: A lonely woman befriends a group of teenagers and decides to let them party at her house. Just when the kids think their luck couldn't get any better, things start happening that make them question the intention of their host.

name: Дедушка нелегкого поведения

name: День драфта
description: At the NFL Draft, General Manager Sonny Weaver has the opportunity to rebuild his team when he trades for the number one pick. He must decide what he's willing to sacrifice on a life-changing day for a few hundred young men with NFL dreams.

name: Друзья рыбака
description: Ten fisherman from Cornwall are signed by Universal Records and achieve a top ten hit with their debut album, "Sea Shanties."

name: Октябрьское небо
description: The true story of Homer Hickam, a coal miner's son who was inspired by the first Sputnik launch to take up rocketry against his father's wishes.

name: Молодые стрелки 2

name: Несмотря ни на что

name: Оливер и компания
description: A lost and alone kitten joins a gang of dogs engaged in petty larceny in New York City.

name: Останься

name: Типа копы
description: Two struggling pals dress as police officers for a costume party and become neighborhood sensations. But when these newly-minted "heroes" get tangled in a real life web of mobsters and dirty detectives, they must put their fake badges on the line.

name: Кошмар на улице Вязов 3: Воины сна

name: Пять легких пьес

name: Толкин

name: Песок

name: Рок-н-рольщики

name: Пятое измерение

name: Человек с запада

name: Провинциалка
description: A Nebraska teen gets more than she bargained for when she sets out for the bright lights of Las Vegas.

name: Игрок
description: A Hollywood studio executive is being sent death threats by a writer whose script he rejected, but which one?

name: Крутой парень
description: A high school senior branded uncool in the ninth grade gets himself expelled so he changes his image to cool kid at the town's other high school.

name: Удачи, Чак!

name: Ужин с придурками

name: Управление гневом

name: Трудная мишень

name: Город тайн

name: Миссия: невыполнима. Смертельная расплата. Часть 2
description: The 8th entry in the long running Mission Impossible franchise.

name: За гранью времени

name: Эксперимент «Ведьма»

name: На берегу реки

name: Теория заговора

name: Плохие слова

name: Cobweb
description: A boy who hears voices in his head decides to unleash them on his abusive parents.

name: Люди-кошки

name: История призрака

name: Космическая одиссея 2010

name: Отчаянно ищу Сьюзэн

name: Рождённый стать королём

name: Манускрипт ниндзя

name: На грани
description: An intellectual billionaire and two other men struggle to band together and survive after getting stranded in the Alaskan wilderness with a blood-thirsty Kodiak Bear hunting them down.

name: Земные девушки легко доступны
description: A Southern California girl befriends three furry aliens after their spaceship lands in her swimming pool.

name: Eileen
description: A woman's friendship with a new co-worker at the prison facility where she works takes a sinister turn.

name: Война миров: Вторжение
description: The adventures of 3 young astronomers and their fight to survive a deadly Martian Invasion.

name: Я женился на убийце с топором

name: Идеальное убийство

name: Джонни Мнемоник

name: Kantara
description: When greed paves the way for betrayal, scheming and murder, a young tribal reluctantly dons the traditions of his ancestors to seek justice.

name: Воображариум доктора Парнасса
description: A traveling theater company gives its audience much more than they were expecting.

name: Дикая штучка
description: A free-spirited woman "kidnaps" a yuppie for a weekend of adventure. But the fun quickly takes a dangerous turn when her ex-convict husband shows up.

name: Смерть среди айсбергов
description: A hunter squares off against a killer whale seeking vengeance for the death of its mate.

name: Волшебная страна
description: The story of Sir J.M. Barrie's friendship with a family who inspired him to create Peter Pan.

name: И грянул шторм
description: The Coast Guard makes a daring rescue attempt off the coast of Cape Cod after a pair of oil tankers are destroyed during a blizzard in 1952.

name: Отныне и во веки веков
description: At a U.S. Army base in 1941 Hawaii, a private is cruelly punished for not boxing on his unit's team, while his commanding officer's wife and top aide begin a tentative affair.

name: Патерсон
description: A quiet observation of the triumphs and defeats of daily life, along with the poetry evident in its smallest details.

name: Единственный выстрел
description: The tragic death of a beautiful young girl starts a tense and atmospheric game of cat and mouse between hunter John Moon and the hardened backwater criminals out for his blood.

name: Эйс Вентура 2: Когда зовёт природа
description: Ace Ventura, Pet Detective, returns from a spiritual quest to investigate the disappearance of a rare white bat, the sacred animal of a tribe in Africa.

name: Conjuring: The Beyond

name: Сын маски
description: Tim Avery, an aspiring cartoonist, finds himself in a predicament when his dog stumbles upon the mask of Loki. Then after conceiving an infant son "born of the mask", he discovers just how looney child raising can be.

name: Шпионские игры
description: Retiring CIA agent Nathan Muir recalls his training of Tom Bishop while working against agency politics to free him from his Chinese captors.

name: Выдуманная жизнь Эбботов

name: Три короля

name: Ледниковый период 4: Континентальный дрейф

name: Водитель
description: A getaway driver becomes the latest assignment for a tenacious detective.

name: Лис и пёс
description: A fox named Tod and a hound named Copper vow to be best friends forever. But as Copper grows into a hunting dog, their unlikely friendship faces the ultimate test.

name: Афина
description: Hours after the tragic death of their youngest brother in unexplained circumstances, three siblings have their lives thrown into chaos.

name: Уайатт Эрп
description: From Wichita to Dodge City, to the O.K. Corral in Tombstone, a man becomes a myth in this thrilling journey of romance, adventure, and desperate heroic action.

name: Рука Бога

name: Моей сестре!

name: Звездный путь: Первый контакт
description: The Borg travel back in time intent on preventing Earth's first contact with an alien species. Captain Picard and his crew pursue them to ensure that Zefram Cochrane makes his maiden flight reaching warp speed.

name: Imaginary Friends
description: Follows a a young girl who goes through a difficult experience and then begins to see everyone's imaginary friends who have been left behind as their real-life friends have grown up.

name: Рога
description: In the aftermath of his girlfriend's mysterious death, a young man awakens to find strange horns sprouting from his forehead.

name: Чтo случилось прошлой ночью
description: A man and woman meet and try to have a romantic affair, despite their personal problems and the interference of their disapproving friends.

name: Любовь и прочие неприятности
description: A thirty-something is still living with his parents until they hire an interventionist to help him graduate out of the house. That's when the fun begins.

name: Мистер Мамочка
description: After he's suddenly laid off, a husband switches roles with his wife. She returns to the workforce, and he becomes a stay-at-home dad, and he has to take care of three young children, a job he has no clue how to do.

name: Апостол
description: In 1905, a drifter on a dangerous mission to rescue his kidnapped sister tangles with a sinister religious cult on an isolated island.

name: Шалун
description: A wannabe-dad mistakes a vertically-challenged criminal on the lam for his newly-adopted son.

name: Вcемирная история, часть 1
description: Mel Brooks brings his one-of-a-kind comic touch to the history of mankind covering events from the Old Testament to the French Revolution in a series of episodic comedy vignettes.

name: Сокровище нации: Книга Тайн
description: Benjamin Gates must follow a clue left in John Wilkes Booth's diary to prove his ancestor's innocence in the assassination of Abraham Lincoln.

name: Экзистенция

name: Корсаж

name: Черепaшки-ниндзя
description: When the world is threatened by an ancient evil, the four adolescent turtles must reunite and overcome their faults in order to stand against it.

name: Техасская резня бензопилой: Начало
description: Before being sent to serve in Vietnam, two brothers and their girlfriends take one last road trip, but when they get into an accident, a terrifying experience will take them to a secluded house of horrors, with a chainsaw-wielding killer.

name: Третий человек
description: Pulp novelist Holly Martins travels to shadowy, postwar Vienna, only to find himself investigating the mysterious death of an old friend, Harry Lime.

name: Особо тяжкие преступления

name: Ниагара
description: As two couples are visiting Niagara Falls, tensions between one wife and her husband reach the level of murder.

name: Его дом
description: A refugee couple makes a harrowing escape from war-torn South Sudan, but then they struggle to adjust to their new life in an English town that has an evil lurking beneath the surface.

name: Камон Камон
description: When his sister asks him to look after her son, a radio journalist embarks on a cross-country trip with his energetic nephew to show him life away from Los Angeles.

name: Чужая Земля
description: Set in the distant future, a female astronaut, shipwrecked on the long-decimated Earth, must decide the fate of the wasteland's remaining populace.

name: Отель Мумбаи: Противостояние
description: The true story of the Taj Hotel terrorist attack in Mumbai. Hotel staff risk their lives to keep everyone safe as people make unthinkable sacrifices to protect themselves and their families.

name: Деннис-мучитель
description: When his parents must go out of town on business, Dennis stays with Mr. and Mrs. Wilson. He is driving Mr. Wilson crazy, but he is just trying to be helpful, even to the thief who has arrived in town.

name: Карусель
description: Fifteen years after his death, a carousel barker is granted permission to return to Earth for one day to make amends to his widow and their daughter.

name: Magazine Dreams

name: Опасные пассажиры поезда 123
description: Armed men hijack a New York City subway train, holding the passengers hostage in return for a ransom, and turning an ordinary day's work for dispatcher Walter Garber into a face-off with the mastermind behind the crime.

name: Гроздья гнева
description: An Oklahoma family, driven off their farm by the poverty and hopelessness of the Dust Bowl, joins the westward migration to California, suffering the misfortunes of the homeless in the Great Depression.

name: Лучший вид
description: Two brothers are pulled into a deal with an organized crime syndicate in Boston.

name: Дом у озера
description: A lonely doctor who once occupied an unusual lakeside house begins to exchange love letters with its former resident, a frustrated architect. They must try to unravel the mystery behind their extraordinary romance before it's too late.

name: Джейн Эйр
description: A mousy governess who softens the heart of her employer soon discovers that he's hiding a terrible secret.

name: Искатели могил
description: For their ghost hunting reality show, a production crew locks themselves inside an abandoned mental hospital that's supposedly haunted - and it might prove to be all too true.

name: Барб и Звезда едут в Виста-дель-Мар
description: Lifelong friends Barb and Star embark on the adventure of a lifetime when they decide to leave their small Midwestern town for the first time - ever.

name: Пленки Андерсона
description: After ten years in prison to protect a mafia family, Duke Anderson is released and he cashes in a debt of honor with the mob to bankroll a caper.

name: Добрый сынок
description: A young boy stays with his aunt and uncle and becomes friends with his cousin, a boy of the same age who shows increasing signs of violent and psychopathic behavior.

name: Девушка из воды
description: Apartment building superintendent Cleveland Heep rescues what he thinks is a young woman from the pool he maintains. When he discovers that she is actually a character from a bedtime story who is trying to make the journey back to her home, he works with his tenants to protect his new friend from the creatures that are determined to keep her in our world.

name: Пассажир
description: An insurance salesman/ex-cop is caught up in a life-threatening conspiracy during his daily commute home.

name: Одиночки
description: A group of twenty-something friends search for love and success in grunge-era Seattle.

name: Лето. Одноклассники. Любовь
description: As a new year at school begins, Lola's heart is broken by her boyfriend, though soon she's surprised by her best friend, promising musician Kyle, who reveals his feelings for her.

name: Скайлайн
description: Strange lights descend on the city of Los Angeles, drawing people outside like moths to a flame where an extraterrestrial force threatens to swallow the entire human population off the face of the Earth.

name: Всем парням: P.S. Я люблю тебя
description: Lara Jean and Peter have just taken their relationship from pretend to officially official when another recipient of one of her old love letters enters the picture.

name: Рэмбо III
description: Rambo mounts a one-man mission to rescue his friend Colonel Trautman from the clutches of the formidable invading Soviet forces in Afghanistan.

name: Кими
description: An agoraphobic Seattle tech worker uncovers evidence of a crime.

name: Роковое число 23
description: Walter Sparrow becomes obsessed with a novel that he believes was written about him, as more and more similarities between himself and his literary alter ego seem to arise.

name: День мертвецов
description: As the world is overrun by zombies, a group of scientists and military personnel sheltering in an underground bunker in Florida must determine how they should deal with the undead horde.

name: Воскрешая мертвецов
description: Haunted by the patients he failed to save, a monumentally burned-out Manhattan ambulance paramedic fights to maintain his sanity over three increasingly turbulent nights.

name: Одно безумное лето

name: День святого Валентина
description: Intertwining couples and singles in Los Angeles break-up and make-up based on the pressures and expectations of Valentine's Day.

name: Тропы
description: A young woman goes on a 1,700-mile trek across the deserts of West Australia with four camels and her faithful dog.

name: Истории семьи Майровиц

name: Возмездие

name: Семьянин

name: Комната желаний

name: Кадавр

name: Убрать перископ

name: Семейка Аддамс

name: Великий диктатор

name: Все псы попадают в рай

name: Маугли: Легенда джунглей
description: A human child raised by wolves must face off against a menacing tiger named Shere Khan, as well as his own origins.

name: Шопо-коп

name: Жена путешественника во времени

name: Кладбище домашних животных
